{"tid":1560140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵遭降級 展望負面","createTime":"2019-09-11T05:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:12:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd590eae4e35def5a1f042bc1114c93bb2ee2485","tid":1560140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190911/20766160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F20766160&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=c0244688\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F20766160&h=c5e2bb93\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190911/20766160</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵遭降級 展望負面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190911/large/1568134698_6968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568134698_6968.jpg&h=c25ea4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n惠譽下調港鐵的長期外幣及本幣發行人評級。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】評級機構惠譽昨晚宣佈下調港鐵（066）的長期外幣及本幣發行人評級，由AA+降至AA，前景展望亦降至負面，即與香港主權信用評級一致。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽指，今次是跟隨香港主權信用評級而一併下調港鐵評級，主要因為港鐵與港府關係緊密，並對港府有策略性重要意義。惠譽又指，如香港主權評級獲上調，同時港鐵持續獲港府大力支持，港鐵的評級會相應調整。反之，若香港主權評級下調，政府對港鐵的控制權被削弱，社會政治環境變差或財務出現違約徵兆等因素出現，則有機會下調對港鐵的評級。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：惠譽指面對社會衝突「港仍有緩衝資本」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n調低中美經濟預測<br />\n<br />\n另外，惠譽調低美國、中國和歐元區等今明兩年經濟增長預測，主因貿易保護主義升溫、中美貿易戰持續及英國硬脫歐風險遞增，令環球經濟增長蒙憂。預測中國今年經濟增長放緩至6.1%，明年經濟增長為5.7%。該行料美國今明兩年經濟增長預測為2.3%和1.7%，兩者較預測前值均低1個百分點。此外，惠譽也降低歐元區今明兩年經濟增長預測至1.1%，料歐洲央行將推出大規模寬鬆措施，10月重啟買債。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n惠譽指面對社會衝突「港仍有緩衝資本」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n震雄高層：接班人早已安排"},{"pid":"1bccecf6dee8488bf0f768ddbe61890250a280f5","tid":1560140,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"會再減"},{"pid":"09b22288835a7916e8642ee3187e112c657e779e","tid":1560140,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:51:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=1f7a8a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"491defd3f7af7ae630fd808f61c4f4f2ef9b77d7","tid":1560140,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447da41ca18f2247376be3602fb316a17d47b942","tid":1560140,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"惠譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"h